Class Vertex<K extends Comparable<K>,V>

java.lang.Object
com.example.romeandvikings.structures.Vertex<K,V>
Direct Known Subclasses:
VertexAdjacentList
public class Vertex<K extends Comparable<K>,V> extends Object
The Vertex class represents a vertex in a graph and stores information such as its key, value, distance, color, and predecessor.
